-- Music Royalty Societies Partly Win Appeal of EU Antitrust Order
-- B y   S t e p h a n i e   B o d o n i
-- 2013-04-12T10:30:37Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2013-04-12/music-royalty-societies-partly-win-appeal-of-eu-antitrust-order.html
National societies that collect
music royalties in most European Union member states  won  their
EU court bid to overturn parts of a decision saying they had
unlawfully colluded.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Stephanie Bodoni in Dublin at 
